Bruhman was founded in 2772 by King Aeon Eternalis.

The reason why he founded the kingdom at such a peculiar date remains unclear. Many think that it was just a coincidence.

Aeon Eternalis was able to ensure world peace by establishing a vast kingdom with policies so fair everyone wanted to follow.

When the kingdom was established, there was the greatest celebration is history.
The Bruhman council decided that from that point on, a new era should start. The Bruhman era had officially begun.

It was a hundred years After Eternalis. (100 A.E.)
The king was well and the kingdom was well. The people of Bruhman were living happily.
All war was forgotten.
Those who seek power had never done so unfairly again.
The stringent yet forgiving policies of Bruhman were taken for granted, and everyone was equal...

Development of technology and other practices was really efficient.
The search for knowledge never ends...

Many many kinds of AI were made, which are in charge of doing all the developing and maintaining.
There just wasn't anything they couldn't do, given that there was enough time.

There was plenty of time.